				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-731025#post-2255168</guid>
				<title>Staff Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-731025/scp-series-3#post-2255168</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2015 03:30:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Noting that a low-rated SCP was deleted as per normal <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/deletions-guide">deletions guideline</a> procedures, but the title included &quot;(WIP)&quot;.</p> <p>For the record, works in progress are <em>not</em> allowed on the mainsite. Drafts and other in-progress works should be written in a <a href="http://scpsandbox2.wikidot.com/">sandbox page</a> and shown to the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/chat-guide">IRC chat</a> and/or the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/c-50864/help:drafts-and-critiques">drafts forums</a> for feedback <em>prior</em> to a mainsite post.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
